x-axis-hover-function: function(x) { var reps = 30; var add = ''; if ($('demographic').selectedOptions[0].getAttribute('auxiliary') == 'M') reps = 32; plus = Math.round(reps*(x - Math.floor(x))); if (plus > 0) add = '+' + plus; return 'Score: ' + Math.floor(x) + add + ' (' + Math.round(reps*x) + ' reps)'; }
